p: α-thujene, α-pinene, myrcene, α-terpinene, p-cymene, β-phellandrene, limonene, and γ-terpinene were found in greater proportion in F1 and F2, this means that are considered more volatile. This coincides with the report by Borgarello et al. and Olmedo et al. [ 7, 9]. According to the analysis of main components performed in this study, the F1 and F2 fractions have no correlation with the biological activities evaluated.
